{"tid":2217714,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"解放軍駐港部隊進行演習 模擬在果洲群島附近發現一艘可疑船隻","createTime":"2020-09-25T15:42:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T18:44:31.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d03d0914dc43ad0e05228909a389efd05cb9961f","tid":2217714,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:42:03.000Z","msg":"解放軍駐港部隊今日組織第三季聯合海空巡邏。<br />\n<br />\n駐港部隊在官方微博上載片段，指陸海空三軍部隊開展聯合搜救、海空巡邏、聯合查證、互為對抗等多項實戰化演練，檢驗駐港部隊履行防務能力。<br />\n<br />\n演練期間，部隊模擬在果洲群島附近發現一艘可疑船隻，特戰小隊坐艦艇攔截和查證。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551707-20200925.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551707-20200925.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8Qfwzje9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=e043f107\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551707-20200925.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=30cbcb46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551707-20200925.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://stream.881903.com/public/b03cf5d9be5b2fa83ac8cc598e8ed98f/2020/09/492df6854cd63f372f952b6258f46591.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstream.881903.com%2Fpublic%2Fb03cf5d9be5b2fa83ac8cc598e8ed98f%2F2020%2F09%2F492df6854cd63f372f952b6258f46591.jpg&h=7310550b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://stream.881903.com/public/666b8deb4e468f5cd519c5a1b1c33846/2020/09/a7d8ac330a7ea1893ab3f3d9ad651a04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstream.881903.com%2Fpublic%2F666b8deb4e468f5cd519c5a1b1c33846%2F2020%2F09%2Fa7d8ac330a7ea1893ab3f3d9ad651a04.jpg&h=9bd66a49&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be07ef216565ca4e26e7076b204452ec10d0439f","tid":2217714,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:43:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/do